public static interface TSRPass.FallbackListener extends com.tencent.mps.tie.api.config.AutoFallbackConfig.FallbackListener
A listener interface for handling fallback events in the super-resolution process.

Implementations of this interface can be registered to receive notifications when a fallback occurs during the super-resolution process. The AutoFallbackConfig.FallbackListener.onFallback(int, int) method will be called when the system triggers a fallback, allowing the user to implement custom behavior in response to the event.
